    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Memory: Dogs - is a cute and calming game featuring pictures of adorable dogs in space. This game will test your memory as you try to find matching pairs of dogs pictures to complete each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the charming atmosphere and improve your memory as the levels become increasingly challenging and exciting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Space Memory: Dogs:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•50 levels<br>•Beautiful space art<br>•Simple controls (mouse)<br>•Achievements<br>•Relaxing music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251610/extras/b381b28c4cd4f821340e09fdb8c400de.poster.avif?t=1745462903\" width=60 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251610/extras/b381b28c4cd4f821340e09fdb8c400de.webm?t=1745462903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251610/extras/2df284dbc3da938bc80cc99a32d9454e.poster.avif?t=1745462903\" width=60 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251610/extras/2df284dbc3da938bc80cc99a32d9454e.webm?t=1745462903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251610/extras/0ada4ddce545e39f36a7ded07d4f8461.poster.avif?t=1745462903\" width=60 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea